reviewText:
I you're into Otaku culture and/or you like to go to Akihabara, this movie is definitely for you.  If you don't know what "Otaku" or "Akihabara" means, this movie is not for you.

It's weird.  It's from Japan.  And I loved it.

I fascinate on movies like these. It's unique and weird. Tho I love movies like that even if it doesn't make much sense. And this movie doesn't well it's random. Get the girl he likes at a coffee shop. That's it. It's a good movie not a love story
